column2: b'Toaru Kagaku no Railgun: Misaka-san wa Ima Chuumoku no Mato Desu kara'

b'Continuing after the Level Upper incident, another phenomenon torments Misaka. A phenomenon called "Someone\'s Watching," its effect feels like the electricity in one\'s body flow backwards. With the help of her friends, Misaka fights against the unknown enemy.'
